Package: collogetr
Type: Package
Title: Collocates retriever
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Gede Primahadi Wijaya Rajeg
Maintainer: Gede Primahadi Wijaya Rajeg <primahadiwijaya@gmail.com>
Description: Generates window-span collocates from raw text corpora.
    The current functionality deals with the sentence-based corpus-input from the (Indonesian) Leipzig Corpora.
    There are also functions to perform collexeme/collocational analysis to determine mutual association strength between a node-word/search pattern and its window-span collocates.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.1)
Imports:
  dplyr (>= 0.7.4),
  tidyr (>= 0.8.0),
  purrr (>= 0.2.4),
  stringr (>= 1.2.0),
  readr (>= 1.1.1),
  tibble (>= 1.4.2),
  rlang (>= 0.1.6),
  stringi (>= 1.1.6),
  assertthat (>= 0.2.0)
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests: testthat,
    covr
URL: https://github.com/gederajeg/collogetr
